T-shirt in their travel bag *

22:47.700 --> 22:49.736
* Beautiful people *

22:49.769 --> 22:52.772
* They've got a price
upon their head *

22:52.805 --> 22:55.842
* I said beautiful people *

22:55.875 --> 22:58.911
* Have got some friends
who just flew in from L.A. *

22:58.945 --> 23:02.014
* Beautiful people *

23:02.048 --> 23:05.051
* They haven't really
much to say *

23:05.084 --> 23:08.120
* I said, people,
they just want to take you *

23:08.154 --> 23:11.190
* People, they just
want to make you *

23:11.223 --> 23:15.127
* People, they just
want to break you down *

23:15.161 --> 23:18.330
* They just want
to take you down. *

