23:31.811 --> 23:34.313
I'm gonna have to get that
to you on Wednesday.

23:34.346 --> 23:35.748
Said you'd have
the money, man.

23:35.782 --> 23:38.250
No, I know I did.
I'm definitely gonna
have it by Wednesday.

23:38.284 --> 23:39.285
Definitely.

23:40.953 --> 23:42.755
I'm gonna have to
give you a touch-up.

23:42.789 --> 23:45.124
What? Well, can it
not be the face?

23:45.157 --> 23:46.893
-It's gotta be the face.
-Why?

23:46.926 --> 23:48.828
It's gotta be somewhere
where people can see it.

23:48.861 --> 23:51.397
-Now, don't flinch, yeah?
-WOMAN: Jason?

23:51.430 --> 23:54.133
Whoa, whoa. Mate, mate.
It's just my mum.

23:54.166 --> 23:56.202
-Hi. I'm Lorraine.
-Nice to meet ya.

24:03.643 --> 24:05.945
-We have to talk, Angel.
-There's nothing to talk about.

24:08.881 --> 24:11.017
-(gunshot)
-What we did was personal.

24:11.050 --> 24:12.184
We broke the rules.

24:12.218 --> 24:14.987
-(rock music) * Yeah *
-(gunfire)

24:15.021 --> 24:16.288
(sirens wail)

24:17.857 --> 24:19.291
ANNOUNCER: Mayans.

